"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1931689-Olympics-2024-gold-medal-Tomas-Machac-Zhizhen-Zhang\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Tomas Machac admitted that he was \\\"really sad\\\" Zhizen Zhang after beating his friend and rival to win Olympic gold in the mixed doubles event.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 144, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Teaming up with Katerina Siniakova,who he is rumoured to still be dating,Machac earned his first medal for Czechia.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 261, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 162, \"end\": 180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate\\u0159ina_Siniakov\\u00e1\", \"score\": 0.9999999989900061, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katerina Siniakova\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate\\u0159ina_Siniakov\\u00e1\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate\\u0159ina_Siniakov\\u00e1\"}, {\"begin\": 253, \"end\": 260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Czech_Republic_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9959269570967444, \"rank\": 0.003894431580429109, \"text\": \"Czechia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Czech_Republic_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Czech_Republic_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It went down to the wire as they beat Zhang and Xinyu Wang of China in a match tiebreak 6-2 5-7 [10-8].\", \"from\": 262, \"to\": 365, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 310, \"end\": 315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinyu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Xinyu\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinyu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinyu\"}, {\"begin\": 324, \"end\": 329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8600451704153597, \"rank\": 0.09013591588857113, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was unusual for Machac and Zhang to be on opposite sides of the net as they regularly play men's doubles together on the ATP Tour.\", \"from\": 367, \"to\": 500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 491, \"end\": 499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATP_Tour\", \"score\": 0.9717203622525011, \"rank\": 0.029098552857945867, \"text\": \"ATP Tour\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATP_Tour\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ATP_Tour\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And after missing out on gold, Zhang joked that their friendship was over.\", \"from\": 501, \"to\": 575, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our friendship is totally broken.\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 611, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He destroyed my Olympic Games\\u2026 everything,\\\" the Chinese star laughed.\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 660, \"end\": 667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9719741286590582, \"rank\": 0.02044126178507972, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The mixed doubles final wasn't the only time Machac thwarted the 27-year-old's hopes in Paris - he also beat Zhang in the men's singles event.\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 824, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 770, \"end\": 775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999976238087, \"rank\": 2.3762117581275016e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zhang continued: \\\"This is a joke.\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 859, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have a really good relationship.\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 895, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even if he beat me twice this week, one time finals and one first round.\\\"\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And there are no hard feelings from the world No.\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"41, who wants to qualify for the ATP Finals in doubles with Machac.\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1087, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have a strong relationship.\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1120, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have really good memories in doubles\\u2026 Our goal is to [be in] Turin,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1202, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1185, \"end\": 1190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turin\", \"score\": 0.9999999991728146, \"rank\": 4.644506180152279e-10, \"text\": \"Turin\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the jokes continued in the locker room as Machac revealed that Zhang tried to kick him out.\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1298, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just in:Tennis star defaulted and booed after throwing racket and swearing at fan  Our community members are treated to special offers, promotions, and adverts from us and our partners.\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1485, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can check out at any time.\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1516, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy    \\\"I came to the locker room to change to the ceremony outfit, and unfortunately they put me in the same locker room (as him).\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was joking like I had to leave, it was funny,\\\" the Czech star said.\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1722, \"end\": 1727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Czech_